      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, preserved in showroom condition. This specimen features the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, which maintains factory-spec compression and flawless transition between the primary and secondary Hitachi HT12 turbochargers. The longitudinal front-midship engine placement ensures a perfect 50:50 weight distribution, complemented by an unmolested four-wheel double-wishbone suspension setup and a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis is free of any structural fatigue, and the cooling system has been meticulously maintained to prevent the thermal degradation common to the platform. With original paint depth and zero oxidation on the undercarriage, this RX-7 represents the zenith of 90s JDM performance engineering.",
